{ A big thank you for the kind words and the grand welcome for my very first Chessable course on 1.b3 :@@EndBracket@@. It just makes my day and heartening to see the positive responses about my course, when people tried it out with success that eventually led to the creation of the 'Cowboy army and the #1b3Cowboy' @@StartBracket@@courtesy of Geert :@@EndBracket@@@@EndBracket@@ which will always unite us wherever we are in the world.I am glad I was able to reach out to many people through my course! It was one of the major reasons which inspired me to do this course on 1.e4 to continue on my journey to share the knowledge which I have acquired... thanks to the in-depth study of openings for all these years! }
