{ Improving over existing games! The idea is to keep pressure on d5 and later on transfer the bishop with Ne2-c3-Bc2, bringing it back into the game. }
8... Qe7+
{ Black has to come up with creative ways if he wants to develop Bg7, since the natural  8...Bg7  is very well met with  9.Qe2+  making a lot of trouble for Black due to his poor development. }
