10... Nbd7
{ The knight will go to f8 where it will help in the defense of the kingside. }
11. Bf4
{ Our advantage is derived from the fact that all our minor/major pieces are superior to the Black side. The plan is to continue with Qd2 and the c3-knight can be sent to f4 via e2. }
