{ Other moves are significantly worse. The c8-bishop plans to make his debut with Be6 next. }
11. Qh5
{ The queen was running out of useful things to do on d5, and hence she changes her trajectory to go for the enemy king. }
11... Be6 { Fighting against Nd5 ideas. } 12. Bb5
{ This was clearly better for white in @@StartBracket@@Koelewijn-Banet ICCF 2020@@EndBracket@@ and we can increase our advantage with Rhe1 followed by Ng5 leading to a better position. }
