, I was as surprised as you!C@@EndBracket@@ Nc6 - I was a big fan of this line as it was suggested to me by my 'Uncle' Lev Psakhis, playing it to confuse opponents during my childhood! But unfortunately, those dreamy days are over and now I have to accept the reality that it is just a bad line leading to a better position... if white knows what he is doing. I am very happy with my find as I feel it is the right way to play for the advantage, but for some reason not very popular! }
