{ We must delay kingside castling to have the option of O-O-O! This devious change of move orders was not considered by Anish. I am reminded of Judit's famous concept of dealing with the long fianchetto which was ' To remove all the pieces along the diagonal' and make it look like it is shooting into thin air. }
