{ Otherwise Black's structure will be in shambles. } 13. e5
{ Using the pin on the d-file to deliver this crushing central advance. } 13...
Nc6 { A nice double attack on d4 and e5. } 14. Qe4 Bg7 { What else? } 15. c5
{ Black won't be able to save the d-pawn. } *

