cxd4
{ This exchange always favors us since the b1-knight can happily go to c3 controlling the central affairs. }
11... O-O
{ One of Black's main ideas will be Bd7-e8-h5 activating his light-squared bishop. }
12. Nc3
{ We have the more pleasant game due to our center control and the backward pawn on e6. }
