{ Normally fianchetto is a very acceptable form of development, but unfortunately against our line, it is not very good and we can get the center or other advantages like better pawn structure. }
4. O-O
{ Priority for development, though alternatively 4.c3 might also give us the advantage or lead to similar territories. }
4... Bg7 5. c3
{ followed by d4 with a big advantage due to our center control and the fianchetto bishop on g7 can't bother our mighty center pawns. }
