cxd5
{ Black has to accept the gift as otherwise, our bishop can happily return to g2 to safeguard our king. }
16. Qxd5+ { A cute double attack on g8 and a8. } 16... Kh8
{ Giving up the rook on a8 to ensnare the queen. } 17. Qxa8 Bb7
{ Black feels that the attack on the a8-queen and the threat of Qc6 would be devastating for us... }
18. Qe8
{ Only move but good enough! A brilliant only move that stops both of Black's threats. }
18... h6 { Making a luft for the king. } 19. Qh5 Qc6
{ The queen and the bishop combo on the long diagonal is always a dangerous combo. }
20. f3 { Black doesn't have the firepower to continue his attack. } *

