6. Nc3
{ We have transposed back to Wesley's 1.e4 Lifetime Repertoires who reached this position via @@StartFEN@@rn1qkbnr/pb1ppppp/1p6/8/3NP3/8/PPP2PPP/RNBQKB1R w KQkq - 1 5@@EndFEN@@  5.Nc3  a6  6.Bg5  ,  but I like our move order as it is more colorful :@@EndBracket@@ and avoids some options for Black. }
