5... f6
{ This over-optimistic break without finishing the development can hardly lead to something good for Black. }
6. Bb5
{ with a clear advantage and we can continue piling up on the e-file by castling to play Re1. }
6... Bd7 { Breaking the pin along the a4-e8 diagonal. } 7. Bxc6
