{ Continuing to avoid the exchanges! One by one, Black's army is about to be thrown back with full force! }
6... Nc5 7. d4
{ Followed by h3 going for the next piece which dared to attack our knight and make him retreat. Black lacks the space and plan to counter our ambitious objectives. Some of the ideas involve c3 strengthening the stronghold on d4 followed by Nf3/Nf4 ideas next. }
