{ Although Black has got the bishop pair...the e4-pawn and the c3-knight together make sure that the bishop will never reach it's full potential. }
9. d4
{ Crashing through in the center leading to a big advantage due to our center control and better development. Additionally we will get rid of the bishop pair due to our overwhelming development advantage. }
