10... Nd7 11. Rd1
{ White has many nice ways to improve the position like b3-Nb2-Nc4 or Nc5 using the pressure along the d-file for getting the knight back into the game. Black must always be very careful about the opening of the position due to the laying dormant bishop pair who are waiting for just that moment! }
