{ Welcome to the jungle! This very strong idea, designed to prepare g4, became popular during the covid/online era and is even more deadly than immediate 5.g4. The golden principle of 'The threat is stronger than the execution' holds here. }
5... Be7
{ This developing move shouldn't be good as it doesn't fight against our plans. }
6. g4 { Of course! This is what we want...after all! } 6... O-O 7. g5
{ Full throttle! } 7... Nh5
{ If the knight retreats to e8, then we continue with Be3 followed by h4-h5 with a powerful kingside pawn storm. }
8. Be3
{ followed by Qe2 and O-O-O to be continued with Nh4-f5 ideas in the future. }
