4... Nc6
{ Black aims to reach the endgame after  5.dxe5  Nxe5  and suffer there :@@EndBracket@@. }
5. Bb5
{ Given a choice, I would rather keep the queens and here it also guarantees a bigger advantage. }
5... Bd7 { Black is hoping for a mass of exchanges. } 6. Bxc6
{ Giving up the bishop pair to maintain the central pressure. } 6... Bxc6 7.
Qe2
{ It is important that we don't close the position with d5 as that will relax the central tension. }
