9... O-O
{ Black's main defensive plan involves Nd7 followed by Bf6, but here it is not so effective since our pieces are well placed. }
10. O-O-O
{ Opposite side castling always favors the one who has better space and attacking chances. Our plan is to continue with g4-g5 and a create a pawn storm on the kingside and there isn't much Black can do about it. }
