8. O-O Nbd7
{ This looks slightly premature as it doesn't put any immediate pressure on e4 and more importantly closes the c8-h3 diagonal. }
9. b3 { Using the time to create the sniper bishop on b2. } 9... Nc5
{ Black still needs one more move to put pressure on e4 leaving us with just enough time to finish our development comfortably. }
10. Bb2
{ The plan is to aim for Re1 followed by h3, Qd2 and Rad1 placing all the pieces harmoniously. After all the preparations are made, we can expand on the center/kingside with f4 or g4. }
