{ Supporting the center and the knight could come under future threats like a6-b5 or c6-b5 threatening to win the e4-pawn with b4. }
3... c6 { This is a bad line and frankly shouldn't challenge us. } 4. Nf3
{ I feel this is at least as good as Wesley's and Sethu's recommendation of 4. f4...if not stronger :@@EndBracket@@. Continuing our development and asking Black to transpose back to Pirc with 4...g6. }
