4... d6
{ Black thinks he has tricked us. ..but little does he know everything which has happened so far is something we have already overseen :@@EndBracket@@. }
5. Bd3
{ A nice place for the bishop where it protects the e4-pawn and the other pieces can develop without having to worry about it. }
