13. c5
{ Showing our enemy who is the boss! Black won't get any time to show his plans! }
13... Nd7
{ Black wants to hold on to his dear knight and one day hopes to re-enter the game as a hero! }
14. O-O { Safety first, mess later! } 14... Be7 15. Kh1
{ A new move. We just keep the king at a safe distance from the future battles and due to our crazy pawn structure with c5-d4-e5 which restricts almost Black's entire army in addition to making the light squares a clear target for our queen and light-squared bishop! We continue our dominance with ideas like Qa4-Rad1 with an undisputed advantage. }
