7. Qxf3 Nd5 8. Qb3 { Continuing to bully Black on the light-squares. } 8... b6
{ How else to save the b7-pawn? } 9. Nc3
{ Developing with tempo and pouring more fuel into the fire! Black's position is a mess due to the weakened light-squares. }
